1
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,120
He's out!

2
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:17,680
He's out!

3
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:18,879
Butler.

4
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:20,400
Lao Jiugui.

5
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,040
This house of yours,

6
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,000
when was it renovated?

7
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,560
How did you know

8
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,719
the house was renovated?

9
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:27,760
The house itself is old,

10
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,319
but the paint

11
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:30,560
and the furniture is new.

12
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,159
Our shopkeeper finished the renovation

13
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:32,959
just three days ago.

14
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,480
So the haunting,

15
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,879
did it also start in these three days?

16
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:38,000
Yes.

17
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:38,959
That's right.

18
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,840
Go check the main beam in the hall.

19
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:43,879
See if there's anything there.

20
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,120
If there is,

21
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,280
bring it down for me.

22
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,519
Go on.

23
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,719
Okay.

24
00:01:59,359 --> 00:01:59,840
Master.

25
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,239
Why are you drinking again?

26
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,439
Shopkeeper Li,

27
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,599
he's not coming back.

28
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:08,280
Found something!

29
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,080
Open it.

30
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,400
Why is it an axe?

31
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,199
Who put this here?

32
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,240
If I'm not mistaken,

33
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,080
you never paid

34
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,560
the carpenter, did you?

35
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,439
We did pay him!

36
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,800
I handed it over myself.

37
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,280
That's strange, then.

38
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,479
Butler,

39
00:02:32,759 --> 00:02:33,599
tomorrow,

40
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,879
have your shopkeeper

41
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,879
and the carpenter

42
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:36,800
who worked for you

43
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,639
come find me at the Bone-Keeping Temple.

44
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,000
For today,

45
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,560
let's leave it at that.

46
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,240
Lao Jiugui,

47
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,080
what'll I do if you leave?

48
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,199
I'm scared.

49
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,280
Dignity.

50
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:51,599
You must keep your dignity.

51
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,039
Move!

52
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,319
Move!

53
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,400
Hurry up!

54
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,240
Don't push me!

55
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:06,000
Lao Jiugui,

56
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,639
it's him,

57
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:08,879
Carpenter Wang.

58
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,240
He's the one who

59
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,039
renovated our house.

60
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,960
So you're Carpenter Wang?

61
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,599
Yes.

62
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,439
Xiao Lian, Dongsheng.

63
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,439
Master.

64
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,199
Speak up.

65
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,680
Why did you use

66
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,639
Yansheng Sorcery?

67
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,080
What Yansheng Sorcery?

68
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,080
I don't understand.

69
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,560
I know.

70
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,599
Yansheng Sorcery is a kind of witchcraft

71
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,800
from The Book of Lu Ban.

72
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:45,719
"Yansheng"

73
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,680
means to loathe and conquer.

74
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,120
Using curses

75
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,120
to suppress people you despise

76
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,039
or evil things

77
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,000
to achieve your own goals.

78
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,800
Sneaking peeks at Master's book again?

79
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,199
You're just a carpenter.

80
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,360
You don't know Yansheng Sorcery.

81
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,400
I...

82
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,479
There's plenty

83
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,280
that I don't know.

84
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:02,879
Fine.

85
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:03,479
You don't know it.

86
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,159
Then today, in front of

87
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,400
the Founding Master,

88
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,479
do you dare to swear it?

89
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,520
Lao Jiugui,

90
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:13,400
I know I was wrong.

91
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,360
But

92
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,680
he sold me fake medicine first,

93
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,240
which caused my mother to die.

94
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,399
I had no choice

95
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,319
but to resort to this.

96
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,040
Carpenter Wang,

97
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:20,680
I...

98
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:21,879
When did I ever sell fake medicine?

99
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,360
Hey,

100
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,000
Lao Jiugui,

101
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,720
don't let him spout nonsense

102
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,480
and talk rubbish here.

103
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:25,959
That was sold by you!

104
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,120
Is this really true?

105
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,199
Absolutely true.

106
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,120
My mother died

107
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,199
from taking his fake medicine.

108
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:30,480
No,

109
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:30,920
Lao Jiugui,

110
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,800
I didn't sell fake medicine.

111
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,040
I couldn't have sold him fake medicine.

112
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,439
Alright.

113
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,639
Shopkeeper Li, I believe you.

114
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:35,160
Good.

115
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:36,240
You didn't sell fake medicine.

116
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:37,879
If...

117
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,680
If you didn't sell fake medicine,

118
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,199
then you can go back

119
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,759
and live in that haunted house.

120
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,240
A clean conscience fears no shadow.

121
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,120
But if you did sell fake medicine

122
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,639
and you go back to live there,

123
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,199
that Yansheng Sorcery

124
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,439
specifically targets bad people.

125
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:52,839
Then you will

126
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,560
in seven days' time

127
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,360
die of a sudden illness.

128
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,079
Even the Great Immortal himself

129
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:56,800
couldn't save you.

130
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,040
You can only stay here with me.

131
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,160
Lao Jiugui,

132
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,639
I'll talk, I'll talk.

133
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:01,639
The thing is,

134
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,519
our Hanging Gourd Hall

135
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,319
really did sell fake medicine.

136
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,040
But the cheap ones are real.

137
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,519
The expensive ones

138
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,079
are fake.

139
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,560
Alright.

140
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:16,879
I understand now.

141
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:18,480
Get up.

142
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:19,680
Wait.

143
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:20,240
That...

144
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,800
Why do you love kneeling so much?

145
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:25,920
Come on.

146
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:29,199
Shopkeeper Li,

147
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,000
you sold fake medicine first.

148
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,959
You have to pay Carpenter Wang

149
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,040
two hundred silver dollars.

150
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,720
And also,

151
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,680
you have to take those fake medicines

152
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,399
and destroy them all.

153
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,360
If you don't destroy them,

154
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,600
I'll report you to the authorities.

155
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,439
Fine.

156
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,680
I agree.

157
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,920
Lao Jiugui, I agree, alright?

158
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:43,560
Alright then.

159
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:43,959
Good.

160
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,199
Carpenter Wang,

161
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,279
when will this cycle of revenge end?

162
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:51,000
Since the dead cannot return,

163
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:54,399
use this money to bury your mother properly.

164
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,439
What do you say?

165
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,199
Okay.

166
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:56,639
I agree.

167
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:57,319
Agreed.

168
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,000
Agreed.

169
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,160
You agree too?

170
00:05:59,160 --> 00:05:59,879
Agree, agree, agree.

171
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:00,800
Then look,

172
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:01,839
I said agree, agree.

173
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,800
Everyone agrees.

174
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:05,680
Lao Jiugui, Lao Jiugui.

175
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:07,879
Get up, get up.

176
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,839
As long as you agree.

177
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,279
That night,

178
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:17,120
I drank that tiger bone wine.

179
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,480
That tiger bone...

180
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,560
It was actually

181
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,519
dog bone.

182
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,160
I...

183
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:27,519
Such a feast today!

184
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,240
Two jugs of wine.

185
00:06:30,439 --> 00:06:31,959
Well, it's the money you earned.

186
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,399
Let's eat, let's eat.

187
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,160
Come on.

188
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:34,680
Master.

189
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,000
Hey, Master,

190
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,279
At Shopkeeper Li's house,

191
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:42,920
why was there

192
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,199
a ghost knocking and a female ghost crying?

193
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,000
See how eager Xiao Lian is to learn?

194
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,839
All you do is eat.

195
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:57,240
Because The Book of Lu Ban says,

196
00:06:57,759 --> 00:06:59,160
smear eel blood on the door,

197
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,680
and ghosts will knock at midnight.

198
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:03,600
Carpenter Wang resented Shopkeeper Li

199
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,680
for selling him fake medicine

200
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,439
that poisoned his mother.

201
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,759
He held a grudge,

202
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,079
so he took eel blood,

203
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,560
mixed it into the paint,

204
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,639
and painted it on the door.

205
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,759
Once the paint dried,

206
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,360
the fishy smell of the eel blood

207
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,519
spread out.

208
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:18,759
The bats from the mountains

209
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,920
smelled it at midnight

210
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:21,800
and crashed into the door.

211
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,519
That sound

212
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,839
sounded just like a ghost knocking.

213
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,160
Then why was the female ghost crying?

214
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,600
The female ghost crying?

215
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,759
Because some small insects

216
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,360
also love that fishy smell.

217
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,959
They flew onto the furniture

218
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,040
and gnawed on it.

219
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,319
That sound

220
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,240
sounded just like a female ghost crying.

221
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:56,439
I wasn't there that day.

222
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:57,360
Imitate it for me, will you?

223
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:10,839
That's the one.

224
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,360
Yes, yes, yes.

225
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,759
The end sounded a bit like a horse neighing.

226
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,600
Master.

227
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:16,639
So in this world,

228
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:18,199
are there really no ghosts at all?

229
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:20,759
There are.

230
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,600
They truly exist.

231
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:30,759
Where?

232
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,000
Right inside everyone's heart.

233
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,320
But always on your tongue.

234
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,519
All right, all right.

235
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,879
Talking ghosts in the dead of night.

236
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,559
Just eat.

237
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,559
Dongsheng.

238
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,759
If you're done eating,

239
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,840
go check on the eternal lamp.

240
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,840
See if it needs more oil.

241
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:03,240
Master.

242
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,000
I'll go too.

243
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,720
From now on, when the kids are around,

244
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,320
could you please consider

245
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,440
Dongsheng's feelings?

246
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,279
A hopeless case, that one.

247
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,200
Coming!

248
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:25,919
Wait,

249
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:26,720
who are you looking for?

250
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,039
Excuse me,

251
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,399
is Lao Jiugui home?

252
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,320
My master went to town for supplies.

253
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,279
They won't be back for a few days.

254
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,799
Is there something you need?

255
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,639
How much farther?

256
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,799
Almost there.

257
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,159
Lady,

258
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,600
you've said "almost there" a dozen times.

259
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,039
If you ignore me,

260
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,320
I'm not going anymore.

261
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:13,480
Pay extra.

262
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:14,759
You have to pay extra.

263
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,399
How much farther?

264
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:23,960
Almost there, almost there.

265
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:28,320
We're here.

266
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,919
Sir, please come inside with me.

267
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,600
This is my poor husband.

268
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,919
I beg you, sir,

269
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,279
to handle his funeral arrangements.

270
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,399
Are you the only one here?

271
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,320
I won't lie to you, sir.

272
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,799
My husband and I

273
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,799
eloped to this place.

274
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,080
We have no one to rely on.

275
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,720
But this morning,

276
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,080
he accidentally fell into the water

277
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,799
and drowned.

278
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:28,759
Don't worry.

279
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:30,519
Leave it all to me.

280
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,519
Then

281
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,399
I'll trouble you, sir.

282
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,120
All right.

283
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,600
Mystic origin of Heaven and Earth,

284
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,480
the root of all energies,

285
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,399
through countless eons of practice,

286
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,440
manifest my divine power.

287
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:06,799
Open the eyes to see all directions,

288
00:12:06,799 --> 00:12:07,720
bright and clear.

289
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,159
Open the nose to smell all scents,

290
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,159
fragrant and sweet.

291
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,399
Open the ears...

292
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:13,759
Open the ears...

293
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,840
How does "open the ears" go again?

294
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,600
To hear all sounds with clarity.

295
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,240
Who's there?

296
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,720
No, no, no!

297
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,320
Stay back!

298
